              project management services from us for both short-term and long-term projects.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center my-3 p-3 rounded bg-white shadow-sm mh-services">
          <div class="px-4 material-icons-round md-36 text-primary ms-n2">school</div>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-around">
            <h4 class="">
              Further training and courses
            </h4>
            <div class="text-muted">
              {{ 'BASEiT' | i18n }} offers an extensive and constantly renewed training offer for IT professionals in
              both technical and management terms. Additional training can be found in either express or extensive
              implementation. Grab this great opportunity right away so you can meet the needs of future challenges
              better tomorrow.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row my-5 py-5 align-items-end">
